#### API Base URL Configuration

```js
// src/config/api.js
const DEV_URL  = 'http://192.168.x.x:5000';   // local machine IP for device testing
const PROD_URL = 'https://ember-coffee-api.onrender.com';

export const BASE_URL = __DEV__ ? DEV_URL : PROD_URL;
```

All API calls import `BASE_URL` from this single file. Switching environments requires changing only this file.

#### AuthContext

Wraps the app and provides `{ user, token, login, logout }`. On login, the JWT is stored via `AsyncStorage` and attached to all Axios requests via a default header:

```js
axios.defaults.headers.common['Authorization'] = `Bearer ${token}`;
```

#### CartContext

Local state only (no backend persistence). Provides `{ items, addItem, removeItem, clearCart, total }`.

